<div class="container py-5">
  <!-- Card Header with Back Button -->
  <div class="card shadow-sm position-relative mb-5">
    <!-- Back Button -->
    <%= link_to interview_questions_path, class: 'btn btn-light rounded-circle shadow-sm d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center position-absolute', style: 'width: 40px; height: 40px; top: 10px; left: 10px;' do %>
      <span class="fs-6">&larr;</span>
    <% end %>

    <!-- Title and Description -->
    <div class="card-body text-center bg-light position-relative">

      <h1 class="fw-bold text-uppercase" style="letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 10px;">
        Placeholder Packet Name
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 14px;">This is a placeholder description for the selected packet. You can quiz yourself on key topics related to this packet.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Card for Question and Answers -->
  <div class="card shadow-sm p-4">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
      <!-- Question and Star Icon -->
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
        <h3 class="mb-0 me-2" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Question</h3>
        <!-- Star Icon -->
        <button class="btn star-toggle p-0" 
                data-star-icon="<%= asset_path('icons/star_icon.svg') %>" 
                data-star-icon-filled="<%= asset_path('icons/star_filled_icon.svg') %>" 
                style="border: none; background: none; margin-top: -6px;">
          <%= image_tag 'icons/star_icon.svg', alt: 'Star Icon', class: 'star-icon', size: '20x20' %>
        </button>
      </div>
      <!-- Question Number -->
      <span class="text-muted" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">2 of 20</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-4">
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
        1. Tender Offer: In a tender offer, the acquirer will publicly announce an offer to purchase shares from existing shareholders for a premium. The intent is to acquire enough voting shares to have a controlling stake in the target's equity that enables them to push the deal through.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5;">
        2. Proxy Fight: Alternatively, a proxy fight involves a hostile acquirer attempting to persuade existing shareholders to vote out the existing management team to take over the company. Convincing existing shareholders to turn against the existing management team and board of directors to initiate a proxy fight is the hostile acquirer's objective, as the acquirer needs these shareholders' votes, which it does by trying to convince the company is being mismanaged.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Answer Choices -->
    <h3 class="text-left mb-4" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Choose Answer</h3>
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-3">
      <div class="col">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg w-100" style="font-size: 0.95rem; white-space: normal;">
          What are synergies and why are they important in a deal?
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg w-100" style="font-size: 0.95rem; white-space: normal;">
          What are the two most common ways that hostile takeovers are pursued?
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg w-100" style="font-size: 0.95rem; white-space: normal;">
          What are some potential reasons that a company might acquire another company?
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <button class="btn btn-outline-dark btn-lg w-100" style="font-size: 0.95rem; white-space: normal;">
          What are the differences among vertical, horizontal, and conglomerate mergers?
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- "Don't Know" Button -->
    <div class="text-center mt-4">
      <button class="btn btn-link text-decoration-none text-muted" style="font-size: 0.875rem;">Don't know?</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>

document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
  document.querySelectorAll(".star-toggle").forEach((button) => {
    button.addEventListener("click", function () {
      const icon = this.querySelector(".star-icon");
      const filledPath = button.dataset.starIconFilled;
      const unfilledPath = button.dataset.starIcon;

      // Check if the current icon is unfilled or filled using a substring match
      if (icon.src.includes("star_icon")) {
        icon.src = filledPath;

      } else {
        icon.src = unfilledPath;

      }
    });
  });
});





</script>
